<br>
An shining example of how to write a meaningful novel, written by a dying man.<br>
<br>
Multiple first-person perspectives, the character development is amazing... overall just an amazing book.<br>
<br>
Don't let the title put you off, if a cynical atheist like me can enjoy it...<br>
